Puppet module: sendmail

# Written by RDK #
# https://github.com/rkhatibi/rdk-puppet-modules

Licence: Apache2

DESCRIPTION:
This module sorts mananges sendmail, but mostly it removes it.

MODULE'S SPECIFIC USER VARIABLES:

USAGE:
# Standard Classes
include sendmail # Install and run sendmail
include sendmail::absent # removes sendmail in prep for adding Postfix

DEPENDENCIES:
Standard classes generally don't need external modules. Puppet 2.6 or better.

OPERATING SYSTEMS SUPPORT (Planned, Development, Testing, Production):
RedHat/Centos 5 : Production
RedHat/Centos 6 : Production
Fedora 14: Production
